* This class specifies a Diffie-Hellman public key with its associated * parameters. * *

Note that this class does not perform any validation on specified * parameters. Thus, the specified values are returned directly even * if they are null. * * @author Jan Luehe * * @see DHPrivateKeySpec * @since 1.4

methods.name: public BigInteger getY()
methods.comment: * Returns the public value y. * * @return the public value y

methods.name: public BigInteger getP()
methods.comment: * Returns the prime modulus p. * * @return the prime modulus p

methods.name: public BigInteger getG()
methods.comment: * Returns the base generator g. * * @return the base generator g
